data.description: Cozy Home in Fruita!  Rare find.  Includes a beautiful private backyard with lots of space for entertaining friends and family. Fully landscaped with mature trees and stepping stones that will make for a wonderful time.  Included with this home is a Breezaire Evaporative Cooler, an oversized 24'x24' garage, a large 33' x 9' patio, and a 24' long pad for your RV.
